---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 444
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=Corruption
  - 423
By: Epictetus
---
The written doctrines of philosophy, if poured into the dirty and
defiled vessel of a false and debased mind, are altered, changed and
spoilt, and turn to urine or anything fouler than that.
